<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ka Buoina Gam</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka buoina gamgaw gam ahin,
 Ka Lal, ka Tanpa mel deihum;
 Luigala A siem gamhaw tawh,
 Ngaiin ka lung a helna e.

[V2]
 Zie gam hawih a chun chawl ingka,
 Lalpa chenna gam hawih achun;
 Vachawl ingka buoina khelah,
 Kei di'n kumsawt gal muonna ah.

[V3]
 2. &quot;Mun siem ingka, Lalpa'n A tii,
 Gingchate kipaka chawlhna'ng;
 Nagaita puongka ka khawvel hin,
 A siem gam chu ka tun tieng leh.

[V4]
 3. Lei ah liengin mun neilo in,
 Gamgaw dahum ah vak mahleng,
 Lalpa'n kei dinga A siemah,
 Chawl ingka luipi gal achun

[V5]
 4. Lasai tiu, Lalpa chawian in,
 Belam No thahsa thokit chun;
 &quot;Hung kit tei ding ka hi&quot; a tii,
 Lawpun lungkhamte kipak un.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>216</hymn_number>
</song>